, and pressing educational contexts of the twenty-first century. In doing so, An Intense Calling maintains that ethics is the core of education because education involves finding better ways of living and being in the world.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mai 2023) 7aEDUCATION / Philosophy, Theory & Social Aspects.2bisacsh  aclassroom.  acurriculum.  aeducation.  aeducators.  aethics in teaching.  aschoolteacher.  asocial justice.  ateachers.  atheories.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2023z97831107973670 cprintz978148754786840uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/978148755562740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781487555627423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781487555627/original  a978-3-11-079736-7  University of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles